The Voyager Dual-Release Adjustable Walker from Keen Mobility is ideal for those looking for a lightweight, easy-to-fold, durable walker.

A key feature of the Voyager is the ability to open the walker arms to two different angles, allowing for varying between-the-arm widths and wider points of entry and angle hand placement. The wheels adjust to face forward at both of these angles.
